item.content:encoded:
Hey guys this was about G7 Cornwall. This beach was the most powerful in the world. The world leaders attending the G7 summit Cornwall, England with PM Boris Johnson from UK urging fellow leaders to “build back better” as the world recovers from the Covid pandemic.

The US president Joe Biden is among those being hosted by Mr Johnson for the three-day meeting, as well as the leaders of France, Germany, Italy, Japan, European and Canada commission president Ursula von der leyen.

This was before the pandemic started early last year, representing most of the world’s biggest economics. It is the first face-to-face summit of the G7 Cornwall.

item.content:encoded:
Hey guys, there was a huge sink hole has appeared in a field in central mexico , it was very big , which is near and threatening to swallow a house

The huge and water filled hole first appeared in the state of PUEBLA on saturday .It was around 5 meters wide . It was continued to get bigger and now stands at around 80 meters in diameter

The local residents warned to avoid area, because the sinkhole has gotten larger hunks of earth have also broken away from the rim and fallen in.

Stay turned for more live updates ….

by Shan Vicky
